Cluster Profiler

gse <- gseGO(geneList=gene_list, 
             ont ="ALL", 
             keyType = "ENSEMBL", 
             nPerm = 1000,
             minGSSize = 5, 
             maxGSSize = 100, 
             pvalueCutoff = 0.05, 
             verbose = TRUE, 
             OrgDb = "org.Mm.eg.db", 
             pAdjustMethod = "none")

dotplot(gse, showCategory=10, split=".sign") + facet_grid(.~.sign)

ridgeplot(gse) + labs(x = "enrichment distribution") + theme_minimal()
